# Architecture Diagrams Directory

This directory contains architecture diagrams and visual representations.

## Diagram Types

- Entity Relationship Diagrams (ERD)
- Sequence Diagrams (authentication flow, data flow)
- Component Diagrams
- Deployment Architecture
- Currency Conversion Flow

## Tools

Recommended tools for creating diagrams:
- Mermaid.js (for embedded diagrams in markdown)
- Excalidraw (for hand-drawn style diagrams)
- Draw.io / Lucidchart (for formal diagrams)
